# Anthropic API key — used server-side for receipt OCR (Claude vision).
# Get one at https://console.anthropic.com/. OCR is optional: without a key
# the app falls back to manual item entry.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model used for OCR (defaults to claude-sonnet-4-6).
# OCR_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
